init should call menu to make main menu
then with main menu it should call a submenu pick the difficulty
then that calls engine.start(mode, difficulty)

-----
e.start()
    set up info, buf, and win
call pretask()

loop:

    e.pretask()
        call ontaskstart()

    ontaskstart()
        spawn task

    validate()
        finished? -> call ontaskend(), call e.posttask()

    ontaskend()
        clean up task

    e.posttask()
        challenge? -> exit
        not? -> call e.nexttask()
